{
  "id": "L07",
  "title": "Making a Simple Appointment by Phone",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "In this lesson, you'll learn how to call a hairdresser ('de kapper') to make an appointment ('een afspraak')."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V01",
      "data": {
        "de kapper": "the hairdresser"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V02",
      "data": {
        "een afspraak": "an appointment"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Goedemiddag",
        "meaning": "Good afternoon"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Ik ben...",
        "meaning": "I am..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Ik wil graag...",
        "meaning": "I would like..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V03",
      "data": {
        "maken": "to make"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V04",
      "data": {
        "komen": "to come"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "To say 'I would like to make an appointment', you combine phrases: 'Ik wil graag een afspraak maken'."
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L07_P01",
      "data": {
        "word": "afspraak",
        "phonetic": "[AF-spraak]",
        "tip": "The 'aa' sound is long, like in the English word 'father'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V05",
      "data": {
        "Wanneer?": "When?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L07_S01",
      "title": "Stating Your Purpose",
      "setting": "You are calling the hairdresser to make an appointment.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Goedemiddag, met de kapper."
        },
        {
          "title": "Greet and state your name",
          "extract_info": {
            "user_name": "Extract the user's name from their message"
          }
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Hallo {user_name}."
        },
        {
          "title": "Say you want to make an appointment"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Oké. Wanneer wil je komen?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Now, let's answer the question 'Wanneer?'. You can suggest a day and a part of the day."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V06",
      "data": {
        "Vrijdag": "Friday"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V07",
      "data": {
        "de middag": "the afternoon"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Vrijdagmiddag",
        "meaning": "Friday afternoon"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L07_P02",
      "data": {
        "word": "Vrijdagmiddag",
        "phonetic": "[VRIJ-dag-mid-dag]",
        "tip": "This is a compound word. Put the stress on the first part: VRIJ-dag."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "The hairdresser will suggest a specific time. 'Uur' means 'o'clock'."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V08",
      "data": {
        "om": "at (for time)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V09",
      "data": {
        "drie uur": "three o'clock"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V10",
      "data": {
        "vijf uur": "five o'clock"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Kan dat?",
        "meaning": "Is that possible?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "What if the time doesn't work? Here's how to say no politely."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Dat kan niet",
        "meaning": "That is not possible"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L07_V11",
      "data": {
        "een andere tijd": "another time"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Kan een andere tijd?",
        "meaning": "Is another time possible?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L07_S02",
      "title": "Negotiating a Time",
      "setting": "You continue the phone call to find a suitable time.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Wanneer wil je komen?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Suggest Friday afternoon"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Vrijdagmiddag om drie uur. Kan dat?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Decline and ask for another time"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Oké. Vrijdag om vijf uur. Kan dat?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Almost there! Let's confirm the appointment and end the call."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Ja, dat is goed",
        "meaning": "Yes, that is good"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "To confirm, it's good practice to repeat the day and time. You can start with 'Dus...' which means 'So...'."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E09",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Dus...",
        "meaning": "So..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Remember, the final proposed appointment is on 'Vrijdag om vijf uur'."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E10",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Dank je wel",
        "meaning": "Thank you very much"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L07_E11",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Tot ziens",
        "meaning": "Goodbye"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L07_S03",
      "title": "Confirming the Appointment",
      "setting": "You are about to finalize the appointment details.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Vrijdag om vijf uur. Kan dat?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Agree to the time"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Oké."
        },
        {
          "title": "Repeat the day and time to confirm"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Ja, dat klopt. Tot vrijdag!"
        },
        {
          "title": "Thank the hairdresser and say goodbye"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Tot ziens."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}